    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "This situation maintains pressure at the primary pulley, ie does not allow the shift cam to control pulley ratio variation, and so, as the vehicle speed decreases, it \"pulls down\" the engine speed with it, giving an engine braking effort.",
